name: phosphorus production, white, liquid | phosphorus, white, liquid | Cutoff, U
description:
ecoQuery: https://ecoquery.ecoinvent.org/3.10/cutoff/dataset/4239/documentation

The functional unit is 1 kg of liquid white phosphorus. Large uncertainty of the process data due to weak data on the production process (based only on literature values).



Raw materials and chemicals used for production, by-products and waste produced, transport of materials to manufacturing plant, emissions to air, energy demand and an estimation of the infrastructure of the plant.
category: C:Manufacturing/20:Manufacture of chemicals and chemical products/201:Manufacture of basic chemicals, fertilizers and nitrogen compounds, plastics/2011:Manufacture of basic chemicals

processDocumentation.geographyDescription: Data used has no specific geographical origin - they represent typical values (Ullmann's). Average values are used for infrastructure and transports.
processDocumentation.technologyDescription: Production from phosphate rock with the aid of the Wöhler process with a yield of 91%.
processDocumentation.dataTreatmentDescription: This dataset has been copied from an original dataset covering the geography RER. The uncertainty has been adjusted accordingly.
processDocumentation.samplingDescription: Process data based on indications in Ullmann's encyclopedia.
